  • iu kin s dng
  • 1 m ngh trn du thuyn Alisa Premier, hng phng Junior Suite Ban Cng
  • Hi trnh tham quan vnh H Long vi cc hot ng th v v hp dn
  • Thng thc cc ba n trn du thuyn vi thc n phong ph v a dng
  • 1 m ngh ti khch sn Pht Linh Hotel H Long, hng phng Superior bao gm n sng

Du thuyn Alisa Premier tiu chun 5 sao l thng hiu c nhiu du khch Vit tin tng la chn bi thit k sang trng tinh t v cht lng dch v nh cao bi i ng nhn vin chu o v t m. Lch trnh tham quan di sn thin nhin th gii vnh H Long cng nhng hot ng si ng, hp dn nh cho kayak, bi li, thm hang hay leo ni chc chn s khin bn ho hng. Bn cnh , nhng ba n ngon c chun b chu o m bo s lm chuyn i ca bn v cng ng nh.

L khch sn 5 sao mi c khai trng thng 7/2020, Pht Linh Hotel H Long c tng 325 phng ngh c thit k thi thng, trang thit b hin i cng tm nhn tuyt p vi mong mun mang li nhng giy pht ngh ngi th gin cho khch hng. Ngoi ra Pht Linh Hotel c v tr rt thun li ngay ti i l H Long Marine, rt thch hp du khch khm ph thnh ph H Long xinh p.

  • Chng trnh ch p dng vi khch hng quc tch Vit Nam.
  • Gi dnh cho 1 khch, 1 phng ngh ti thiu 2 khch. Trng hp 1 khch 1 phng s p dng ph ph phng n.
  • Gi p dng n 31/12/2020 v c linh hot chuyn i sang cc nm tip theo c km theo ph ph.
  • Gi p dng cho giai on thp im (01/09/2020 31/12/2020) v c p dng ph thu cho giai on cao im v cc ngy l, tt, cui tun
  • Yu cu nng hng phng (c ph thu) s c p dng theo tnh trng phng trng ca du thuyn v khch sn
  • Khch hng c th linh ng ph thu thm 01 m ti khch sn. Vui lng lin h vi nhn vin CSKH c h tr
  • Chng trnh khuyn mi khng kt hp vi cc chng trnh u i, khuyn mi khc ca tu.
  • Chng trnh u i khng hon, khng hu.
